com.bigdata.sparse

Interface ITPV

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TPS.TPV

    public interface ITPV
    a Timestamped Property Value is a single {property, timestamp, value} tuple for some schema as read from the SparseRowStore.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson

        Returns:
